See 'connection.hxx' how to create your connection. This file should be used only
    internally to resolve circular dependency between Server and Connection.

                            --+
    connection.hxx            | internal only
      |        \            --+
      |         v           --+
      |      server.hpp       |
      |         /             | public
      v        v              |
    connection.hpp            |
                            --+

'connection.hpp' is a file to be used externally in your projects.

How to define your server you can learn from 'server.hpp'.

